name: Music Kit | Juelz, Floorspace
description:
This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP. The Music Kit replaces the following music: - Main Menu - Round Start and End - Map Objective - Ten Second Warning - Death Camera

Need Floorspace? This massive music kit from Juelz’s debut album contains neo-rave synths, gritty bass lines, and hard hitting trap drums. Floorspace has been reimagined for Counter-Strike 2, and the MVP anthem “Gossip” makes players want to set up—then drop—an LED wall.
